Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.21,0:00:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.91,0:01:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Greetings to all of you at the ICPO.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.67,0:01:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I am L.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.25,0:01:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether the guilty party\Nis an individual or a group,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.05,0:01:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a strong possibility\Nthat they are Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.26,0:01:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira, I've got a pretty good idea\Nwhat your motivation might be,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.51,0:01:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can guess what you hope to achieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.01,0:01:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,However…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,what you're doing right now is evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.39,0:01:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] You… you bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.14,0:01:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Now… try to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.52,0:01:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-I am justice!\N-What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.35,0:01:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I protect the innocent\Nand those who fear evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who will become the god\Nof a new world that everyone desires!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:01:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,L…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.86,0:01:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.90,0:01:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kira and Light] I will hunt you down\Nwherever you're hiding,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.32,0:02:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and I will eliminate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.41,0:02:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I am…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I am…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kira and L] … justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.29,0:02:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,DEALINGS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.42,0:02:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[car horns honking]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,SERIAL MURDER\NSPECIAL INVESTIGATIONS HQ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.29,0:02:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] All right. Let's start\Nwith the tip line reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[detective 1] Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Up to this point, we've received\N3029 responses about the murders
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,via telephone and e-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of these have been curious citizens\Nand prank calls,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but there are 14 people who claimed\Nto either know Kira or who have seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All 14 accounts were followed up on\Nand carefully documented.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.19,0:02:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,However, nobody could provide\Nany information
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that wasn't already publicly available.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.32,0:02:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And lastly, this week\Nthere were additional 21 people
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,who called in claiming to be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[indistinct chatter]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm… [clears throat]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,0:02:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[detective 1] We didn't want\Nto rule anything out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we followed standard procedure\Nand created files for all 21 of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Uh huh. All right.\NOn to the victim reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[detective 2] Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:03:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Upon further investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.34,0:03:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,we have confirmed that information\Nof the heart attack victims
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,was in fact publicly available in Japan\Nimmediately prior to their deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Also,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.81,0:03:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,concerning L's request that we investigate\Nthe time of death for each victim,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.27,0:03:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,we found that all of them occurred
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,between the hours of 4 p.m. and 2 a.m.\Non weekdays, local time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,with 68 percent of them\Noccurring between 8 p.m. and 12 a.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.53,0:03:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Weekends and holidays appeared\Nto be the exception to this rule
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,as the times of deaths vary\Nmuch more widely than during the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[L through voice modifier]\NThat information
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is extremely relevant for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It suggests that,\Ngiven the times of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.71,0:03:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,our suspect could very well be a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.01,0:03:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Based on the fact\Nthat Kira is only killing criminals,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's safe to assume
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that he is driven\Nby a very idealistic notion of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's highly possible he may even aspire\Nto be some sort of godlike figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We're dealing with an individual
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,who has a very childish concept\Nof right and wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:03:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[muttering]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Of course,\Nthis is mere speculation at this point,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but still, I recommend you re-examine\Nany assumptions you've made
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,as to whether or not our suspect\Ncould be a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We must consider every possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that's the shortest route\Nto finding and arresting Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, continue with your report.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.88,0:04:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Does anyone else have\Nsomething they'd like to add?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.51,0:04:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] What is it, Matsuda?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Um… well, I'm not saying this\Nto support Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,or to condone the murders, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,in the last few days throughout the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but especially here in Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,we've observed the dramatic decrease\Nin the number of violent crimes committed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[muttering]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Well, I suppose it makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.86,0:04:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We've suspected\Nsomething like that would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.99,0:04:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[unsettling music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Well, that about sums up\Nour report for today. L?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Thank you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:04:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel we're one step closer\Nto finding Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I go, I'm afraid I have\None additional request to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is directed\Nto the teams investigating the victims,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,TV news, and internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like you to go back
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.68,0:05:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and take a closer look at the exact way
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,in which the victims' identities\Nwere made public.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Be as thorough as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] In particular,\NI want to know if photos of the victims
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,were made available to the public\Nin Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[through voice modifier]\NI leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Matsuda] Chief!\N-Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like you could use one of these.\NSleepy much?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. Thank you. That'll do the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel all these late nights\Nare starting to take their toll.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami gulps] Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,About what I said earlier at our meeting…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now that I think about it, um,\NI'm sure everyone already knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody said it'll be easy\Nto speak the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but it has to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.30,0:05:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially when it is something\Nthat isn't easy to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Having said that,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:05:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,if you'd gone on to say\Nthat we should commend Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,for doing such a great job\Nof reducing violent crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,then yes, I might have\Nhad a little problem with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] Oh, no. No, I wouldn't.\NThat would never happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.57,0:06:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami laughing] Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sayu] I knew I can count on you, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, so do you think you're ready\Nto try a few on your own now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[doorbell rings]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sounds like Dad's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Sachiko] Welcome home, dear.\N-[Yagami] Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He's home really early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't you at least\Ntry the last problem by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sayu] I will, but maybe after dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Helping your sister with her homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If the police try to come after me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty confident I've got something\Nthat'll give me the advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.03,0:06:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, glad you could join us for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You hungry, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's been a long day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[chopsticks clattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Light, tell me.\NHow are your studies going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Everything's okay, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.71,0:07:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. He's at the top of his class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My big brother is a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.64,0:07:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my son!\NWe're all proud of you, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Is everything okay, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You look tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.93,0:07:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not able to say too much about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but this case I'm working on now\Nis really tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-Well, well. Daddy's a policeman.\N-[keyboard clacking]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And that must be the reason\Nwhy you're so confident?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's easy for me to hack\Ninto Dad's computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on a home network,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,so I can copy the files I need\Nwithout leaving a trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.83,0:07:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, I can keep track\Nof their investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, isn't that interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the police are already\Nbeginning to suspect a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk cackles]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that means you're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If the cause of death is written within\N40 seconds of writing the person's name,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.03,0:08:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,it will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If the cause of death is not specified,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the person will simply\Ndie of a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.25,0:08:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,After writing the cause of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,details of the death should be written\Nin the next six minutes and 40 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.46,0:08:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That sound right to you, Ryuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's your point?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, if I write\Nheart attacks as the cause of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,then I should be able to write down
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,all the details including\Ntime of death afterward, shouldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I will be able to provide you\Nwith more entertainment now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[tense music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[inmate grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-[grunting]\N-[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.76,0:09:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Inmate 148, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.89,0:09:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.82,0:09:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting, gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[inmates] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,TASK FORCE HEADQUARTERS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I-- I don't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Another 23 victims yesterday?\NAre these confirmed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[detective] Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The day before there were\Nanother 23 victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's killing one off,\Nevery hour on the hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering that this new pattern\Nhas been going on for two weekdays…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.13,0:09:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It does punch some holes in the theory\Nthat our suspect is a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe not.\NAnybody can skip two days of school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.47,0:09:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] You're missing the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huh?\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] It does appear less likely now\Nthat Kira is a student,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's not the message he's sending\Nby doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask yourselves, why every hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And why are all these victims in prisons
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,where they are sure to be\Ndiscovered immediately?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not other criminals like before?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe Kira is telling us
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that not only can he kill from a distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but he can also\Ndetermine the time of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[muttering]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] But something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as we began to suspect\Nthat Kira might be a student,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the pacing of the killings changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,As if to contradict that theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.26,0:10:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Too convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This can only mean that Kira\Nhas access to police information.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a direct challenge to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I'd say L is probably\Nstarting to sweat a little by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll really make his job difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is that I've deliberately left\Nabout 50 criminals alive
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,for times like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If L is as good as they say,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,by now, he should be starting to suspect
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,someone with connections to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] So, Kira has found a way
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.37,0:11:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,to obtain information\Nfrom the Task Force headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is one fact that cannot be ignored.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.46,0:11:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But what does he get out of all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he hoping to achieve in the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one thing I don't get.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Showing them\Nyou have connections to the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,makes it easier for them to find you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,than when they\Njust suspected you a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.48,0:11:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my real agenda is…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to get close to L,\Nso I can eliminate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you gonna do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.24,0:11:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You still don't understand human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In this world, there are very few people\Nwho actually trust each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.91,0:11:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's no different for the police,\Nyou know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's especially important
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,is that L and the investigators\Ndon't trust each other at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you trust someone\Nwhose name and face you don't even know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:12:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,When L discovers that I'm somehow\Ngetting confidential information,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll be obligated\Nto start investigating the police
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.72,0:12:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to find the source of the leak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When that happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll only be a matter of time\Nbefore the police start resenting L.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.27,0:12:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,On the surface it will appear
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.27,0:12:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that L and the investigation team\Nare working together to try to catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.19,0:12:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But in reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,L will investigate the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and they will be investigating L.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.78,0:12:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the one who is going to find L.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can let the police do that for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.99,0:12:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And when they do,\Nthat's when I'll eliminate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,TASK FORCE HEADQUARTERS
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.64,0:12:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,LETTER OF RESIGNATION
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[detective 1] With all due respect, Chief,\Nwe're resigning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.02,0:12:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[muttering]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[detective 1] We demand that you assign us\Nto a different case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.07,0:13:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, you can have our badges\Nright here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? You're good cops!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because we value our lives, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[detective 2] If what L says is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira has some ESP-like power
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.45,0:13:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,that somehow allows him to kill people\Nindirectly from anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[detective 3] Well, if I were Kira, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd probably wanna try and get rid\Nof the people who are trying to catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's face it, he knows he will be\Nsentenced to death if he's caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[detective 1] We all sat here and watched
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.09,0:13:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,when L decided to pull that media stunt\Nand challenge Kira to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it was all very impressive\Nat the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but then again,\NL never had to show his face
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,or reveal his name for that matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you recall L's last request?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked that we take a closer look
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,at how these victims' identities\Nwere made public
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and specifically, to determine\Nwhether photos of the victims
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,were available to the public\Nprior to their deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.49,0:13:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it turns out he was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.07,0:13:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Every single one of those victims'\Nnames and photos
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,were broadcast to the Japanese public,\Nand then they died!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.41,0:13:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike someone we know,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.75,0:13:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,we're out there investigating this case
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.54,0:14:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,wearing police IDs\Nwith our names and photos on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.21,0:14:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody with a computer\Ncan find out who we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.67,0:14:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't hide our faces!\NWe're out in the open!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.26,0:14:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, the truth is,\Nwe could be killed by Kira at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,For these reasons,\Nwe refuse to continue working this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.89,0:14:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.23,0:14:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop! All of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[door closes]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.32,0:14:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to solve this problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.11,0:14:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,we must establish the concept
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.17,0:14:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that X squared equals large X.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.87,0:14:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now pay attention\Nbecause this is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we tackle\Nmore complex quadratic equations,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,we have to start thinking\Nof large X's value
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,as simply the multiple of two integers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.21,0:14:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's apply this concept\Nto our first problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.39,0:14:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[Watari] We brought the FBI to Japan\Nfour days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They are fully operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,As requested, they're now\Ngathering intel on the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:14:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-[L] And this is the complete list?\N-[Watari] Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There are 141 people in the police force
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,who have access to classified information\Nregarding the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sure that somewhere in this list
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of the police officers\Nand the people closest to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,we will find our suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.95,0:15:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,SOICHIRO YAGAMI\NDETECTIVE SUPERINTENDENT
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.29,0:15:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,NPA HEAD OF SPECIAL INVESTIGATIONS\NSERIAL MURDER CASE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.62,0:15:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Light, you got a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already told you, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't talk to me in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times do I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll talk, you just listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.01,0:15:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to hear me,\Nyou can plug your ears or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all,\NI don't have anything against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.18,0:15:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually think the notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't have been picked up\Nby a better person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here 'cause I have to stick around\Ntill the Death Note is finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.48,0:15:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,or I see you die, whichever comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But make no mistake, Light,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.11,0:15:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not on your side or L's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Yeah. Well,\NI knew that much already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.62,0:15:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never hear me say anything
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,about whether what you're doing\Nis right or wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.62,0:16:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not here to support you\Nor give you my opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a spectator,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but as your roommate,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I might have a few things to say\Nnow and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this about, Ryuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you\Ntelling me all this stuff now, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that I'm no ally of yours,\Nor Kira's, if you prefer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The only reason I'm going to tell you this
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,is because, personally,\Nit is starting to creep me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Get to the point already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.02,0:16:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You are being followed by another human.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He's watching you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really starting to get on my nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I realize there's no way he can see me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but because I'm always following\Nbehind you wherever you go,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.26,0:16:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm constantly being watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:16:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] That's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to get rid of him\Nas soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would be following me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[door squeaks]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean L is already starting\Nto suspect the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's gonna investigate the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.28,0:17:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll need a lot of resources\Nand manpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he has as many\Nas 50 people on the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see how they could ever figure out\Nthat I'm Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't look like anything other\Nthan your average high school senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.46,0:17:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But the longer I let this person\Nkeep following me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.42,0:17:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the greater the chance\Nis they'll figure out who I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Above all…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.43,0:17:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I need my stalker's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I figure that out,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can get rid of him for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Ryuk] Light.\N-[Light] Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.27,0:17:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] I'm gonna let you in\Non a little secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes a Shinigami and a human\Nwho has a Death Note different?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there are two things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And why do Shinigami
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:17:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,have to write the names of humans\Nin their Death Notes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:17:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You got any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.32,0:18:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not. Why would I know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you sure are talkative today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,0:18:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because we are able\Nto take human lifespans for ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait, what do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say you have a human\Nwho is due to live until the age of 60
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and a God of Death wrote\Nthat this person would die at 40.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sixty minus 40 equals 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.18,0:18:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now those 20 years\Ntaken from someone in the human world
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,are added to that God of Death's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.10,0:18:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it means that\Nas long as we don't slack off,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,even if someone\Nwas to shoot us in the head,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,or stab us in the heart with a knife,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,a God of Death cannot die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how many names\Nyou write in your Death Note,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,your lifespan will not increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.91,0:18:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the first difference
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,between gods of death and humans\Nwho possess a Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles] That's something\Nabout Shinigami
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.09,0:18:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that I haven't heard before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty interesting stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:18:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The second difference between us
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,will probably be\Nof even greater interest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Though this has less to do\Nwith lengthening life
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.39,0:19:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and more to do with cutting it short.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean cutting it short?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.89,0:19:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinigami can tell what the person's name\Nis by just looking at their face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We know instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And do you have any idea why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.98,0:19:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Because through a Shinigami's eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,a human's name\Ncan be seen above their head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,we see their lifespan as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Their name and lifespan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,LIGHT YAGAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] That's right. I'm able to see\Nyour name and lifespan right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.04,0:19:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[tense music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] If I converted that to human time,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I could tell you\Nhow many years you've got left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no way I'd ever tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I may have a big mouth,\Nbut even I wouldn't go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.39,0:19:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinigami never have to worry\Nthat they won't be able to kill a person
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,just because they don't know their name,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and every time we do take a life,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.77,0:19:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,we always know exactly how many years\Nwe are going to receive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.61,0:20:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Our eyes just aren't the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is the difference\Nbetween you and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,However…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,if a Shinigami drops his Death Note\Nand a human picks it up,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.45,0:20:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,he can grant that human\Nthe eyes of a Shinigami,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.14,0:20:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but only if a deal is made,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.25,0:20:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,one that has been with us\Nsince ancient times.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.84,0:20:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's the deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The price for having the Shinigami's eyes…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,is half of that person's\Nremaining lifespan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Half of my remaining lifespan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,if you are supposed to live\Nanother 50 years, it'll be 25.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was one more year, then six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.65,0:20:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And since you've made it clear\Nyou're not on anyone's side,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.87,0:20:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and won't help me out,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.99,0:20:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't just give me\Nthe names of people I want to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.20,0:20:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, you're saying that I can't\Nsimply borrow your powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd have to pay for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.92,0:20:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.09,0:21:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a key part of the code\Nthat all Shinigami are bound by.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say this once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me half your remaining lifespan,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.76,0:21:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll give you the Shinigami Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.39,0:21:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If I agree…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be able to know everyone's name\Njust by looking at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.98,0:21:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had that power,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.23,0:21:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the Death Note\Nwould only be easier to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what'll it be, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.90,0:21:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.63,0:21:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[music concludes]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.43,0:21:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme song playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.12,0:22:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[music concludes]